        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="text">
                  <p><strong>Golang关键字</strong> keywords</p>
<p><code>break</code>	<code>default</code>	<code>func</code>	<code>interface</code>	<code>select</code>	<code>case</code>	<code>defer</code></p>
]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="text">
                  <p><strong>Golang关键字</strong> keywords</p>
<p><code>break</code>	<code>default</code>	<code>func</code>	<code>interface</code>	<code>select</code>	<code>case</code>	<code>defer</code></p>
<!-- more -->
<p><code>go</code>	<code>map</code>	<code>struct</code>	<code>chan</code>	<code>else</code>		<code>goto</code>	<code>package</code>		<code>switch</code></p>
<p><code>const</code>	<code>fallthrough</code>	<code>if</code>	<code>range</code>	<code>tyge</code>	<code>continue</code>	<code>for</code>		<code>import</code></p>
<p><code>return</code>	<code>var</code></p>
<p><strong>Package 别名</strong></p>
<p><code>import f "fmt" // f.Println()</code></p>
<p><code>import . math //Sqrt(4.0)</code></p>
<p><strong>Golang命名</strong></p>
<p>🐫驼峰命名，一般首字母小写，大写具有特殊含义(程序调用外部包时，只有大写开头才能被调用)</p>
<p><strong>int</strong> <strong>范围</strong></p>
<p>int类型会根据操作系统变化，在32位的操作系统中，int类型是32位，在64位操作系统中同理</p>
<p>int的取值范围：</p>
<p>int: -2^31 ~ 2^31-1 <strong>or</strong> -2^63 ~ 2^63-1</p>
<h3 id="array">Array</h3>
<p><strong>Array 声明</strong></p>
<div class="code-toolbar"><pre class=" language-go"><code class=" language-go">var arrName [length]type
//声明长度为length，类型为type，名称为arrName的数组
var arrName = [length]type{1,3,2}
arrName := [length]type{true,flase}
</code></pre><div class="toolbar"><div class="toolbar-item"><span>Go</span></div><div class="toolbar-item"><button>Copy</button></div></div></div>
<h3 id="selice"><strong>Selice</strong></h3>
<p><strong>Selice声明🎤</strong></p>
<div class="code-toolbar"><pre class=" language-golang"><code class=" language-golang">var seliceName = []type{elements...}
//声明并初始化
seliceName := make([]type,length,capacity)
//make([]type,2,2) == make([]type,2)
</code></pre><div class="toolbar"><div class="toolbar-item"><span>Golang</span></div><div class="toolbar-item"><button>Copy</button></div></div></div>
<p>​</p>
<p><strong>selice排序</strong></p>
<p>📂使用sort包对selice进行排序</p>
<div class="code-toolbar"><pre class=" language-golang"><code class=" language-golang">sort.Ints(a []int) //递增排序
sort.Sort(sort.Reverse(sort.IntSelice(a []int)))	//递减排序
</code></pre><div class="toolbar"><div class="toolbar-item"><span>Golang</span></div><div class="toolbar-item"><button>Copy</button></div></div></div>
<div class="code-toolbar"><pre class=" language-golang"><code class=" language-golang">sort.Float64s(a []float64)
sort.Sort(sort.Reverse(sort.Float64sSelice(a []float64)))
</code></pre><div class="toolbar"><div class="toolbar-item"><span>Golang</span></div>]]></content>
